c: 20
v: 97
t: "(Musa) naboola mbu; “mana rula tsia,! ne toto kalaba khwiwe mubulamu bwao bwokhushialo okhuboola mbu: “olandilakhwo tawe’” ne toto oli nende indakano eyilalifunakwa tawe. Ne khahengekhwo Nyasaye wuwo owotsilile okhumulaama, toto khwitsa okhumusamba mana khulamwibisia munyanza akoreremwo"